rows.label: tlk70000161_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Me is nameless wanderer, travel
through high and dry and low and wet
and cold and also warm places.

rows.label: tlk70000161_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Life of traveler is lonely one, so is
much relief when there is chance of
talk with otherpon.

rows.label: tlk70000161_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Is such relief talking to friends, must
reward somehow. Here, take this Aux
Core me found lying in nearby lake.

rows.label: tlk70000161_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Is just fancy paperweight for
non-Driver, so not much use keeping.
Happy to give away.

rows.label: tlk70000161_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Me think it should be just right
for Blade who really into smashing
and brawling.

rows.label: tlk70000161_01_msg0007
rows.name:
How friends getting on with Assist Core
that me give as gift?

rows.label: tlk70000161_01_msg0008
rows.name: Sorry, was not meaning to pry...

rows.label: tlk70000161_01_msg0009
rows.name:
Is just...me have strangest feeling,
it maybe most Ultimate of all item.
Make sure friends keep for life!
